data.description: Welcome to your dream home in picturesque Cape Cod! Imagine waking up to the serene views of a lush green golf course right from your window. This stunning split-level raised ranch offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. Newly discovered hardwood floors that have been under carpet since the home was built add warmth and character to every room. With 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, there's plenty of space.  Brand new luxury vinyl plank flooring added to kitchen. You'll adore the spacious living areas perfect for hosting gatherings with loved ones. And with a finished lower level featuring an additional bedroom, bathroom, and den, there's even more room to accommodate guests or create your own personal retreat. Outside, mature plantings surround the property, providing privacy and a peaceful ambiance. Whether you're enjoying a morning cup of coffee on the patio or hosting a barbecue with friends, you'll love spending time in the beautiful outdoor spaces. Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional Cape Cod home with golf course views. Septic systems tank and D box need to be replaced at buyers expense.  Quote received for $8,000. Easy to show.
